 color=#A62A2A>(12/19/02 2:45:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3323.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Damn dirty Yantis</span><hr size=1> Naari my friend,<br>
<br>
 When you come to these boards you need to put the weapons down and put them back in your holster. Of course you are entitled to your opnions but you need to start approacing my comments with a less defensive stance buddy.<br>
<br>
 I am merely provided arguments to WHY people who play this game would see an attraction in buying a horse for real money. I NEVER said that is what I would do or am doing. I won't buy anything for real money and although I too would like that horse I am never going to afford it and am certainly not paying real cash for it. <br>
<br>
For those of you accusing me of being  loot dude, I can say you don't know me at all. For those that know me know that I play this game for fun and to talk to online friends i have aqquired on this server. I just mentioned reasons for why this would be an attraction and gave an example of how someone  like me who plays regularly but not regularyl enough to afford a 100k horse would be tempted by such. Is this perfectly clear guys??<br>
