Theres no need to flame bro <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :hat --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/pimp.gif ALT=":hat"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=naari@firionavie>Naari</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/19/02 12:25:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3323.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Damn dirty Yantis</span><hr size=1> You know Noggy. It is entirely possible you are a swell guy. In your other post on guilds, the eventual point you got to, that guilds should band together so they can accomplish more together than individually is something I certainly can agree with.<br>
<br>
However, it isn't what came across in the original post and I altogether disagree that there are too many guilds. As I said there, I would like to see even more guilds.<br>
<br>
Here, you took the viewpoint that buying items with real world money is ok. Many on this server feel very differently. In fact, even on blue servers, many feel differently. On this server in particular, with its supposed RP preferred orientation, many feel that this is just another part of the slippery slope that would lead us to be just like the other servers. Speaking for myself, that is NOT something I want to see happen.<br>
<br>
Tolerance is held up as a virtue now days, in and of itself. But frankly tolerance of some things leads inevitably to those things becoming common place. I'm not going to be tolerant of the viewpoint you expressed here for that reason.<br>
<br>
The truth is that we do apparently see things very differently. From what you have said it is abundantly clear to me that I would never feel comfortable in your guild. There are probably many activities I would enjoy doing with you. Being in a guild together probably isn't one of them.<br>
<br>
Judging from these two topics and your responses, I am honestly puzzled why you want to play on this server.<br>
<br>
By the way, neither this or the original post in this thread is a flame. You have a right to take the viewpoints you did and express them. I do strongly disagree in both cases. I made my case why.<br>
<br>
I agree with those who are worried about the effect farming plat and items for sale in real world money causes. I didn't need to repeat their arguments so I didn't. I do think I addressed why it is completely unnecessary in the first place.<br>
<br>
I understand the temptation for buying something like a horse with real world money. But I am afraid that if that temptation is allowed to flourish and grow, we will have sown the seed of this servers destruction. In my mind, that would be a real shame. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=bjond>Bjond</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1779<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/19/02 8:12:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3323.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> One of the things I look for ..</span><hr size=1> .. in a guild is non-tolerance of e-bay: buy/sell anything in game for RL cash and get booted out of guild.  I far prefer to play with people that like playing the game as opposed to those that let the game play them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=3323.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=3323.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3323.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.threadControl?topicID=3323.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Comman